.SH FILES
main.h  
Header file containing function prototypes and necessary includes.

.SH SEE ALSO
[main.h(3)](main.h), [_get_token(3)](main.h), [execute_command(3)](main.h), [get_command_path(3)](main.h), [check_if_full_path(3)](main.h), [free_tokens(3)](main.h)

.SH BUGS
No known bugs.

.SH EXAMPLES
To execute a command, type its name followed by any arguments and press Enter.


